title: csrf_token
pid: da117ad2-e805-4510-b511-d218e16f3da3
body: |2-
  Use these around to prevent "cross site request forgery" attacks.

  "all POST forms that are targeted at
   internal URLs should use the {% csrf_token %} template tag"

  e.g.
    <form action="..."
          method="post">
      {% csrf_token %}
      ... do stuff ...
    </form>
